34
00:03:27,249 --> 00:03:29,251
Kenapa dengan budak itu?

35
00:03:29,668 --> 00:03:31,211
Adakah kamu kenal dia, Tsukihiko?

36
00:03:35,591 --> 00:03:37,092
Jangan cuba lari!

37
00:03:37,342 --> 00:03:39,428
Saya akan kejar kamu sehingga ke hujung neraka...

38
00:03:39,428 --> 00:03:41,847
dan kelar kepala kamu dengan pedang saya!

39
00:03:42,222 --> 00:03:44,516
Saya takkan lepaskan kamu!

40
00:03:45,267 --> 00:03:47,394
Apa yang berlaku?

41
00:03:47,436 --> 00:03:48,812
Adakah kamu mabuk?

42
00:03:49,062 --> 00:03:51,398
Budak, jauhkan diri kamu dari lelaki itu.

43
00:03:51,398 --> 00:03:52,482
Tak boleh.

44
00:03:52,482 --> 00:03:54,276
Beri saya rantai penggari.

45
00:03:54,276 --> 00:03:55,444
Tolong, saya merayu.

46
00:03:55,444 --> 00:03:56,778
Jangan cakap lagi, lepaskan dia!

47
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:58,155
Tolonglah, jangan buat begitu.

48
00:03:58,155 --> 00:04:00,324
Tiada siapa boleh mengawal dia kecuali saya.

49
00:04:00,324 --> 00:04:01,408
Ke tepi!

50
00:04:01,408 --> 00:04:02,701
Tak, tolong berhenti!

51
00:04:02,743 --> 00:04:05,204
Oh, Tuhan. Apa yang terjadi kepada mukanya?

52
00:04:05,204 --> 00:04:06,747
Adakah dia sudah hilang akal?

53
00:04:06,955 --> 00:04:08,916
Heret budak tu keluar.

54
00:04:08,916 --> 00:04:10,292
Tolong berhenti.

55
00:04:10,292 --> 00:04:12,961
Saya tak nak dia bunuh siapa-siapa.

56
00:04:12,961 --> 00:04:14,630
Jangan masuk campur.

57
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:16,548
Saya merayu.

58
00:04:16,632 --> 00:04:17,674
Tak guna.

59
00:04:17,674 --> 00:04:20,719
Kalau kamu terus melawan...

60
00:04:27,851 --> 00:04:28,977
Sihir Darah.

61
00:04:29,144 --> 00:04:30,145
Aroma Darah Khayalan.

62
00:04:30,145 --> 00:04:31,146
Mimpi Visual.

63
00:04:32,731 --> 00:04:34,942
Apa bau harum ini?

64
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,945
Apa corak-corak ini?

65
00:04:40,572 --> 00:04:41,657
Apa yang sedang berlaku?

66
