Saya tak nampak apa-apa di sekeliling saya!

67
00:04:44,451 --> 00:04:45,994
Adakah ini sejenis serangan?

68
00:04:46,119 --> 00:04:47,621
Kalau ini serangan, habislah.

69
00:04:49,414 --> 00:04:50,999
Bau itu semakin kuat.

70
00:04:59,883 --> 00:05:00,968
Kamu masih...

71
00:05:01,718 --> 00:05:03,470
