72
00:05:04,346 --> 00:05:07,349
walaupun dia sudah bertukar menjadi iblis.

73
00:05:08,183 --> 00:05:10,227
Malah kamu mahu tolong dia.

74
00:05:11,979 --> 00:05:15,232
Apa-apa pun, saya akan tolong kamu.

75
00:05:16,149 --> 00:05:17,526
Kenapa?

76
00:05:17,776 --> 00:05:18,777
Kamu.

77
00:05:19,069 --> 00:05:20,445
Bau harum kamu...

78
00:05:21,405 --> 00:05:22,406
